      javax.sound.midi.Track addOnOtherChannel(Song song, javax.sound.midi.Track track, byte channel, boolean startAtZero)
      add a MidiPart (transformed to MidiEvents) to a track but on an other channel if afterwards something is added, it will start after the last event on the channel playing longest(if startAtZero is not toggled) always make sure you are not adding MidiEvents with ticks equal to already existing MidiEvents, as the result will sound horrible
